lead_paragraph: Hillary Clinton, who leads the pack of potential Democratic 2016 presidential contenders, defended Obamacare on Wednesday but added she was open to "evidence-based changes" in the program, CNN reported.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Defends Obamacare, but Open to Changes: Report
